`},{path:"/article/lo7fbj1s/",title:"使用 wsl2 安装深度学习环境",categoryList:[{id:"8c5f70",sort:10003,name:"深度学习"}],tags:["Deep Learning","WSL"],createTime:"2024/12/16 20:50:52",lang:"zh-CN",excerpt:`<blockquote>
